title: Document AI - RawDocument
abstract:
# Document AI - RawDocument
Payload message of raw document content (bytes).| JSON representation             |
|:--------------------------------------------------------------------|
| { "content": string, "mimeType": string, "displayName": string } || Fields  | Fields.1                                                |
|:------------|:-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| content  | string (bytes format) Inline document content.A base64-encoded string.                                |
| mimeType | string An IANA MIME type (RFC6838) indicating the nature and format of the content.                             |
| displayName | string The display name of the document, it supports all Unicode characters except the following: *, ?, [, ], %, {, },', \", , ~, = and : are reserved. If not specified, a default ID is generated.
